---
import ContentLayout from '../../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="GM Tools"
  summary="Practical templates, randomizers, and reminder sheets for keeping sessions sharp, strange, and emotionally coherent."
  eyebrow="Table tools"
  audience="gm"
  spoilerLevel="major"
  theme="gm"
  robots="noindex,nofollow"
  gmGate={true}
>
  <section class="two-column">
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Session Prep Template</p>
      <ul>
        <li>What changed since last session?</li>
        <li>Which NPC needs the strongest voice reminder?</li>
        <li>What image, lyric, or symbol should recur tonight?</li>
        <li>What pressure clock is closest to advancing?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Session Recap Template</p>
      <ul>
        <li>What promise was made?</li>
        <li>What fear surfaced?</li>
        <li>What did the players misunderstand in an interesting way?</li>
        <li>What should echo later?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-column">
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Random Thinny Effects</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The room smells like rain from another year.</li>
        <li>Everyone hears one word from a dead voice.</li>
        <li>One shadow moves a beat too late.</li>
        <li>A map briefly redraws itself.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Todash Stress Table</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Nosebleed and ringing teeth</li>
        <li>Lose the name of one object for an hour</li>
        <li>See an ally standing where they are not</li>
        <li>Gain a truth you wish you did not know</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-column">
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Ka Complication Builder</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The successful choice costs time</li>
        <li>The failed choice reveals character instead of stopping progress</li>
        <li>The right action wounds the wrong relationship</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section content-prose">
      <p class="section-label">Demo Session Checklist</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Explain tone and safety tools</li>
        <li>Offer pregens with two-sentence summaries</li>
        <li>Teach Ka before the first danger roll</li>
        <li>End on one image that sells the campaign</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</ContentLayout>
